<p>We&#8217;ve also thrown a blank one in there too:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/swot-analysis-template-blank-720.png" alt="swot analysis template blank" width="720" height="543" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-56684" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/swot-analysis-template-blank-720.png 720w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/swot-analysis-template-blank-720-480x362.png 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw" /></p>
